{
  "stem": "4830.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a fascist party continuously increasing numbers-- never, mind you, passing the 24%, 25% membership.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the relationship was separate, we lived a separate life, but there were exceptions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were friendships, there were inter-marriages, as well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in-- with a small percentage of people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It really never came up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody could believe that anything like what has happened, happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even in 1944, when the Germans already occupied Hungary, we had no idea what is going on exactly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew that things are not that terribly good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But prior to that, nobody in our immediate family was thinking of leaving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was, as I told you, it was accepted as a way of life, and we-- looking back in history-- we always had our ups and downs as Jews during the centuries, and we did not really think that there would be any place which would be better.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That-- that was just one thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even those who wanted to leave, there was no place to leave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As you probably know, the United States and Canada was closely shut.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The only places that accepted Jewish refugees was China and some countries in South America.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this was only after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Boy Scouts.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a Boy Scout from age 6 to 10.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had a tremendous career as a Boy Scout, because eventually, I became the commander of our unit.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was a very disappointing year, because just in the middle of the year, the new law came in that Jews cannot be Boy Scouts, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] except in separate Boy Scout groups.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, the squeeze was gradual.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
